Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Input.Touch

Class TouchCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Input.Touch.TouchCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TouchLocation>, ICollection<TouchLocation>, IList<TouchLocation>

    public class TouchCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements IList<TouchLocation>
    Provides methods and properties for accessing state information for the touch screen of a touch-enabled device. Reference page contains links to related code samples.
